                    <div>Windows</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </center>
    </div>
    
    <div class="detail two">
        <div class="image"/>
        <div class="text">
         <div class="title">Sync Gateway</div>
         <div class="description">Synchronize on-device Couchbase Lite with Couchbase Server in the cloud.</div>
      <div class="long-description">Configure your cloud in one page of programmable sync code. Add data routing and more with a scalable sync tier.</div>
         <ref href="../../docs/src/guides/sync-gateway/set.xml">Learn more</ref>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="detail dark three">
        <div class="image"/>
        <div class="text">
         <div class="title">Couchbase Server</div>
         <div class="description">A high performance, scalable, always-on JSON database in the cloud.</div>
      <div class="long-description">Submillisecond, high-throughput reads and writes give you consistent high performance. Couchbase Server is easy to scale out, and supports topology changes with no downtime.</div>
         <external-ref href="http://www.couchbase.com/couchbase-server/overview">Learn more</external-ref>
        </div>
    </div>
    
